{"tid":1114793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★唔捱得！】30後 情緒困擾墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-04-18T16:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T07:30:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f2d1281206e7b5edcdd5b4ce38a10c4e2c352abe","tid":1114793,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T16:36:38.000Z","msg":"香港仔利東邨發生跳樓自殺事件。今日(18日)傍晚約6時，一名姓簡老婦(87歲)，被途人發現倒臥在東興樓對出行人路。<br />\n<br />\n由於途人目睹有私家車快速駛離現場，懷疑私家車車主肇事逃逸，遂報警求助。警方接報到場，證實簡已經死亡。經初步調查，證實簡從東興樓28樓一單位墮下，事件不涉及交通意外。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，簡一直飽受情緒病困擾，警方在現場檢獲其遺書，稱因生活問題不開心尋死。警方認為事件無可疑，簡死因仍待驗屍確定。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190418/bkn-20190418203751040-0418_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190418%2Fbkn-20190418203751040-0418_00822_001.html&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dMv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=30ed6791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190418/bkn-20190418203751040-0418_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a226be7687ef966206f4367bdc45bb10fd039cb9","tid":1114793,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T16:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6979dabf2d8c164e3e66d4e594ca0ecebda8809","tid":1114793,"uid":247184,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T16:40:44.000Z","msg":"老實講80幾係呢個逼癲人既社會，死又唔死得，周身病痛，又無咩可以享受，出街人多車多，想寧靜少少去遠d郊外都未必去到，長命真係反而係一個煎熬"},{"pid":"da37d774ed918773c4b37a44053776d4aebccdb2","tid":1114793,"uid":86509,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T22:54:51.000Z","msg":"真心唔明點解冇安樂死<br />\n成個社會建立係垃圾制度度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至少六十五歲有安樂死<br />\n社會問題少八成"},{"pid":"4747f616e891d3f0ec11ab03aaa8596a06523e51","tid":1114793,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:05:25.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"0b23f60